IMAPAccount mercandev
Host imap.porkbun.com
User aydin@mercan.dev
PassCmd "secret-tool lookup user aydin@mercan.dev service smtp"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore mercandev-remote
Account mercandev

MaildirStore mercandev-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/mail/mercandev/
Inbox ~/.local/mail/mercandev/Inbox
Subfolders Verbatim

Channel mercandev
Master :mercandev-remote:
Slave :mercandev-local:
Expunge Both
Create Both
Patterns *
SyncState *
